text: Tobias Martin Hayles-Docherty (born 30 January 1999) is an English professional footballer who last played as a midfielder for Walsall. ==Playing career== Hayles-Docherty came through the Walsall youth team to first make the first team bench in April 2017. He made his EFL League One debut as a 68th- minute substitute for Maziar Kouhyar in a 1–0 defeat to Port Vale at the Bescot Stadium on 25 April 2017. On 28 September 2018, Hayles-Docherty was sent out on a one-month loan deal at Halesowen Town until 3 November.
